[SN]TITLE[SN]
Family come face to face with grizzly bear

[SN]FIRST-SENTENCE[SN]
A family in America have had a close encounter with a grizzly bear.

[SN]RESTBODY[SN]
30 June 2015 Last updated at 08:54 BST
The bear at Yellowstone National Park strolled right up to their car and jumped on to the front, before walking round it.
The family recorded the bear for a few minutes before it got bored and wandered off.
